<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1268880 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--1062x598.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--1062x598.jpg 1062w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--640x360.jpg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--1536x864.jpg 1536w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--320x180.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--281x158.jpg 281w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--562x316.jpg 562w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--531x299.jpg 531w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--487x274.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--974x548.jpg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.--600x338.jpg 600w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Bobby-Brown-Jr.-.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Bobby Brown Jr., the son of singer Bobby Brown is dead at the age of 28. He was found dead at his home in Los Angeles on Wednesday after officers were called to a “medical emergency,” the Los Angeles Police Department said. He was pronounced deceased at the scene. There is no suspicion of foul play in relation to his death. His death is coming five years after the death of his half-sister and eight years after his stepmother Whitney Houston drowned in a bath. From back row left: Pops Brown, Whitney Houston, Tommy Brown, Bobby Brown Jr., La’princia Brown, Bobby Brown and Bobbi Kristina Brown. The photo was taken for the family’s show on Bravo, Being Bobby Brown, when Bobby Jr. was 13 The Brown family has been plagued with sorrow and grief for years. The late Houston who was an iconic songstress was married to the senior Brown until 2007. She and Brown had a tempestuous 15-year marriage that was plagued by drug abuse, violence and infidelity. She died on February 11, 2012, from accidental drowning in a bathtub after taking cocaine and Xanax. The coroner also ruled heart disease as a contributing factor. Three years after her death, Brown and Houston’s daughter Bobbi Kristina Brown also died in a tragic manner. The 22-year-old was found unresponsive and unbreathing in a bathtub at her Roswell, Georgia home. She died six months later at a hospital where she was being treated. “He worked hard to hold his head up and stay sober and … he genuinely wanted a happy healthy life with his family more than anything else,” Gordon’s attorney, Joe Habachy, said. “My heart goes out to the family and friends Nick leaves behind and to any other families dealing with the losses and heartache caused by drugs.”